After cloning into Termux, here's the complete launch sequence:

# 🔥 STEP 1: Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Sosnac/CrypTrus2.0.git
cd CrypTrus2.0

# ⚡ STEP 2: Run automated setup
bash setup.sh

# 🚀 STEP 3: Quick scan (choose one):

# Option A: Basic scan
python3 cryptrus2.0.py -t 192.168.1.0/24 --all

# Option B: Interactive menu
./termux/launcher.sh

# Option C: Full command with all modules
python3 cryptrus2.0.py -t 192.168.0.0/24 --scan --detect --iot --vuln --save -v

# Option D: After setup, use symlink
cryptrus2.0 -t 192.168.1.0/24 --all